(firstQuint)Treatment Outcome Using Vivaer Stylus to Treat Nasal Airway Obstruction.

 This is a non-significant risk, prospective, non-randomized study to evaluate subjective and objective measures of nasal obstruction both before and after treatment with the Vivaer Stylus.

 The Stylus is used to deliver radiofrequency (RF) energy to the nasal valve area to improve symptoms in those diagnosed with nasal airway obstruction.

